utch, quoted upon request.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/6/56DCF0EC7CAAE4B19EB55BE9679865E8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">StikPIn</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Stick Pin Attachment</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Stick pin attachment in place of standard butterfly or rubber clutch.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.60 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/8/A8D36170AE4B4BED687BC64068F453F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">ZP</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Zipper Pull</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Zipper pull attachment in place of standard butterfly or rubber clutch.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.15 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Lapel Pin Presentation Packaging</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/C/5CB5026BEF305214CD534BD9CC8DA394.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Cards-3.5X2</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Custom Printed Cards</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Custom card with lapel pin inserted. Each card individually poly bagged. Pricing includes full color, one sided card 2&quot; x 3.5&quot; size. Other sizes and full color imprints available, call for pricing. Lapel pin(s) priced separately.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.95 each · $0.65 each · $0.30 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/8/D/8D1B232E078E99C69D574C54FEDCC564.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">2PcBox</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Lapel Pin Presentation Box</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">2-Piece plastic presentation box with clear cover and black interior platform case.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.60 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/2/D/2D605B2485E6112BACBEAC5458192D51.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">SmBox</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Velour Pin Box</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Small Velour Box for Lapel Pins up to 1.25&quot;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$2.50 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/0/B/0B2AD60C226FDE42F2723F14B68DBA03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Pouch Small</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Small Velour Drawstring Pouch</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">For emblems up to 2&quot;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.90 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Lapel Pins Die Struck Soft Enamel (3/4&quot;). Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">ISE75</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>20 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">300</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}